ch.bfh.btx8053.w2016.white.HVmanager.model

Class ExternalPerson

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.bfh.btx8053.w2016.white.HVmanager.model.Person
      • ch.bfh.btx8053.w2016.white.HVmanager.model.ExternalPerson
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Connectable

    @Entity
public class ExternalPerson
extends Person
implements Connectable
    This class create an external person who extends from Person.
    It has additional a description, a private address and/or a business address.
    An external person can have different types, who are define in the enum-class ExternalPersonType.
    Author:
    nallm1, umern11, nedot1, heldf1, caldf1
